{"tid":2207214,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[DLLM]美國法官：WeChat禁令含糊　或頒布初步禁制令","createTime":"2020-09-18T04:31:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T07:50:01.000Z","uid":144626,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"af81f1e7aef44745ddd924f64d80d75d2ff94ed6","tid":2207214,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T04:31:15.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普8月6日簽署行政命令，限制騰訊 （00700） 旗下WeChat與美國企業或個人交易，禁令將於周日（20日）生效。 不過，美國地方法院法官Laurel Beeler在聽證會上表示，由於WeChat禁令過於模糊過於含糊，願意應「美國微信用戶聯盟」（U.S. WeChat Users Alliance）的請求頒布初步禁制令，但未作出最終決定。<br />\n<br />\nBeeler在聽證會上表示，很同情禁令給受影響的人們帶來的焦慮，又稱WeChat是這些人唯一的交流方式。<br />\n<br />\n政府代表律師Michael Drezne在聽證會上表示，法官不應因總統的命令含糊而禁止有關行政命令，因為在商務部澄清禁止交易之前，該命令不會得到執行。"},{"pid":"3989220eef7da28a44a7281f9bb36f5655a5c887","tid":2207214,"uid":19527,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T04:33:11.000Z","msg":"咁就清晰啲囉<br />\n全部唔比用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"999805ec8c1e0f6c056601888422202f3ff6e099","tid":2207214,"uid":144626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T04:33:58.000Z","msg":"Laurel Beeler<br />\n<br />\n又係加洲, 山火呀, 燒得烈d, 燒死晒d左膠喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78f77023669ae671928ff5a1868e21b1bf775a0a","tid":2207214,"uid":244332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3989220eef7da28a44a7281f9bb36f5655a5c887","tid":2207214,"uid":19527,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T04:33:11.000Z","msg":"咁就清晰啲囉<br />\n全部唔比用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T04:34:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"